<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>World News Today: Read the latest world news headlines, Current International breaking news world wide. In depth analysis and top news headlines world wide.</description><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>2026-05-19T11:11:01+05:30</lastBuildDate><atom:link type="application/rss+xml" rel="self" href="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/296589292.cms"/><copyright>Copyright:(C) Tue, 19 May 2026 11:11:01 IST Bennett Coleman &amp; Co. Ltd, http://in.indiatimes.com/policyterms/1554651.cms</copyright><docs>http://syndication.indiatimes.com/</docs><image><title>World News, Today World News, Latest International News, World Breaking News, Trending News of World - Times of India</title><url>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/507610.cms</url><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link></image><item><title><![CDATA[Experts stunned by a forgotten medieval book in Rome hiding oldest English poem]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131191545.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Researchers in Ireland have unearthed the oldest known English poem, "Caedmon’s Hymn," dating back to the 7th century. This remarkable discovery, found embedded within a 9th-century Latin manuscript in a Roman library, predates previous earliest known copies by three centuries, offering new insights into the early spread of the English language.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/experts-stunned-by-a-forgotten-medieval-book-in-rome-hiding-oldest-english-poem/articleshow/131191545.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/experts-stunned-by-a-forgotten-medieval-book-in-rome-hiding-oldest-english-poem/articleshow/131191545.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T11:02:53+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131191597,imgsize-885101.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Buried for 3,000 years: Egypt’s Lost Golden City of Luxor reveals an ancient world frozen in time]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131190918.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/buried-for-3000-years-egypts-lost-golden-city-of-luxor-reveals-an-ancient-world-frozen-in-time/articleshow/131190918.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/buried-for-3000-years-egypts-lost-golden-city-of-luxor-reveals-an-ancient-world-frozen-in-time/articleshow/131190918.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T10:24:57+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131190930,imgsize-121400.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Iran plans €50mn bounty on 'gambler' Trump, 'child-killer' Netanyahu: Report]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131190414.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran's parliament is considering hefty financial rewards for assassinating US President Trump and Israeli PM Netanyahu, escalating tensions after recent strikes. Lawmakers aim to formalize bounties, viewing these leaders as responsible for the death of Supreme Leader Khamenei. This move shifts threats from rhetoric to official parliamentary action, with warnings of wider retaliation.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-plans-50-million-bounty-on-gambler-donald-trump-child-killer-netanyahu-for-whoever-sends-them-to-hell-report/articleshow/131190414.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-plans-50-million-bounty-on-gambler-donald-trump-child-killer-netanyahu-for-whoever-sends-them-to-hell-report/articleshow/131190414.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T10:14:52+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131190775,imgsize-1787027.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Cuba: US military action would lead to a ‘bloodbath’]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131190657.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Cuban President Miguel Diaz-Canel has issued a stark warning about the potential fallout from U.S. military actions, predicting a 'bloodbath' and significant turmoil across the region. He emphasized that Cuba is not a threat to its neighbors. This statement arises in light of rumors surrounding Cuba’s supposed procurement of over 300 military drones, coupled with plans to attack U.S. interests.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/cuba-us-military-action-would-lead-to-a-bloodbath/articleshow/131190657.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/cuba-us-military-action-would-lead-to-a-bloodbath/articleshow/131190657.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T10:12:51+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131190742,imgsize-1081612.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Growing furniture: This UK couple is growing actual chairs from living trees]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131190436.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/growing-furniture-this-uk-couple-is-growing-actual-chairs-from-living-trees/articleshow/131190436.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/growing-furniture-this-uk-couple-is-growing-actual-chairs-from-living-trees/articleshow/131190436.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T10:14:13+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131190561,imgsize-2222480.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[DOJ announces $1.8bn fund to compensate Trump allies]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131190540.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[The Trump administration has rolled out the 'AntiWeaponisation Fund', a staggering $1.8 billion initiative aimed at reconciling claims from allies of the former president, who contend they have faced unjust scrutiny from the Justice Department. This fund is a direct result of Trump’s decision to drop his extensive $10 billion lawsuit against the IRS, signaling a shift in strategy.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/doj-announces-1-8bn-fund-to-compensate-trump-allies/articleshow/131190540.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/doj-announces-1-8bn-fund-to-compensate-trump-allies/articleshow/131190540.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T10:04:09+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131190583,imgsize-644083.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Vax crisis inherited, had no measles shots in stock when we took office: BNP govt]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131189808.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Bangladesh faces a severe measles crisis with hundreds of child deaths and thousands infected. The current government claims it inherited a complete lack of vaccines, blaming previous administrations for the outbreak due to halted immunization programs.  Authorities are now racing to vaccinate, while the High Court considers barring officials from leaving the country amid investigations into vaccine shortages.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/vax-crisis-inherited-had-no-measles-shots-in-stock-when-we-took-office-bnp-govt/articleshow/131189808.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/vax-crisis-inherited-had-no-measles-shots-in-stock-when-we-took-office-bnp-govt/articleshow/131189808.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T09:07:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Ahsan Tasnim</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131189856,imgsize-212676.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Pak sends new Iranian peace proposal to US]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131189040.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Iran has initiated a bold peace proposal to the United States, channeled through Pakistan, in a bid to halt the West Asia conflict and prioritize the lifting of maritime sanctions. Talks on nuclear issues would be postponed under this new agreement.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pak-sends-new-iranian-peace-proposal-to-us/articleshow/131189040.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pak-sends-new-iranian-peace-proposal-to-us/articleshow/131189040.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-19T08:22:44+05:30</pubDate><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131189213,imgsize-766565.cms"/></item><i